Author: kdanica95
Text: 24 year old currently living with parents. I feel you. It SUCKS especially when you want to do something adult-ish (cause let’s be real, we are lmao) and they treat you like you’re 17 (cause let’s be real, we’re still “under their roof”)  If I wasn’t saving as much money as possible for university I’d be out like a light ahahaha
